subSubSection.paragraph:
Mxp3
: Ischium with well-developed distal spine on flexor margin; extensor margin unarmed; crista dentata with 25 or 26 denticles. Merus subequal in length to ischium, with 3 or 4 acute granules (
holotype
) or spines (
paratype
) on flexor margin, proximal longer than others; extensor margin unarmed. Carpus spineless along extensor margin.
